Rating: 2
This recipe is a good starting point, but it needs what other's have suggested (lime juice) and also a little more kick. Try adding some pasilla or chilis de arbol, ground up. Also, a handful of toasted pepitas ground up with the tomatillos would add some nice texture and depth.

